USB Touchscreen driver for Eleduino 7 inch tft lcd display with touchscreen


Notes:

Instead of unloading the usbhid-module using the load.sh script, you can create a modprobe configuration file to prevent usbhid from claiming the touchscreen device.

/etc/modprobe.d/usbhid_touch.conf

options usbhid quirks=0x0eef:0x0005:0x0004
